attributes.description: This dashboard shows Audit events collected by the PingFederate integration.

params.markdown:

[**PingFederate**](/app/integrations/detail/ping_federate/overview)

- **Audit**
- [Admin](#/dashboard/ping_federate-4e1a3b90-8da8-4d5d-89e7-5c49fb4a3541)

**Overview**

The audit dashboard features various metrics, including the Top 10 Users by Roles, Top 10 Hosts, Top 10 Sources, and traffic categorized by event type. It also displays events over time, the Top 10 IPs with failed login attempts, and the Top 10 Clients. Additionally, it provides an overview of the total number of users, total audit events, and a comparison of SSO success versus failures.
